Interface AwsCredentialsTaskWithPrefix


  • public interface AwsCredentialsTaskWithPrefix

      • getAccessKeyId

        @Config(value="aws_access_key_id")
 @ConfigDefault(value="null")
Optional<String> getAccessKeyId()
        Gets the AWS IAM access key ID configured.

        It is available only when the authentication method is set to: "basic" or "session".

        Returns:
        The AWS IAM access key ID configured. (For example, AKIAIOSFODNN7EXAMPLE)
        See Also:
        Managing Access Keys for IAM Users
